---
layout: base.njk
title: "Tratamientos en AnyLopez Clínica Estética — Benidorm"
description: "Ocho especialidades, un único oficio. Catálogo editorial de tratamientos faciales, corporales, inyectables y aparatología en AnyLopez Clínica Estética, Benidorm."
---

<style>
  /* ─── HERO ─────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .svc-hero {
    padding: 96px 0 72px;
    background: var(--ivory);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .svc-hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(40px, 6.5vw, 76px);
    line-height: 1.05;
    margin: 12px auto 24px;
    max-width: 880px;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .svc-hero h1 em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--terra);
  }
  .svc-hero p.lead {
    font-size: clamp(16px, 2vw, 19px);
    color: var(--text-mid);
    max-width: 620px;
    margin: 0 auto 36px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .svc-hero-meta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 18px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-mid);
    margin-top: 28px;
  }
  .svc-hero-meta strong { color: var(--text); font-weight: 600; }
  .svc-hero-meta span.dot { color: var(--sand-mid); }
  .svc-hero-stars { color: var(--gold); letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 15px; }

  /* ─── INDEX GRID ──────────────────────────────────── */
  .svc-index {
    padding: 24px 0 96px;
    background: var(--ivory);
  }
  .svc-index-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 32px;
  }

  /* ─── CATEGORY CARD (editorial) ───────────────────── */
  .svc-cat {
    position: relative;
    display: block;
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 2px;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    transition: transform 0.4s var(--ease), box-shadow 0.4s var(--ease), border-color 0.4s var(--ease);
  }
  .svc-cat:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    border-color: var(--terra);
  }
  .svc-cat-img {
    position: relative;
    height: 280px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .svc-cat-img img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    transition: transform 0.7s var(--ease);
  }
  .svc-cat:hover .svc-cat-img img { transform: scale(1.04); }
  .svc-cat-img::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(26,18,8,0) 0%, rgba(26,18,8,0.45) 100%);
  }
  .svc-cat-num {
    position: absolute;
    top: 20px;
    left: 24px;
    z-index: 2;
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
  }
  .svc-cat-flag {
    position: absolute;
    top: 20px;
    right: 24px;
    z-index: 2;
    background: var(--terra);
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 6px 12px;
    border-radius: 2px;
  }
  .svc-cat-body {
    padding: 32px 32px 36px;
  }
  .svc-cat-eyebrow {
    font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--terra);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    display: block;
  }
  .svc-cat-name {
    font-size: clamp(24px, 3vw, 32px);
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    color: var(--dark);
  }
  .svc-cat-desc {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--text-mid);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .svc-cat-trat-list {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .svc-cat-cta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--terra-dk);
    border-bottom: 1px solid currentColor;
    padding-bottom: 4px;
    transition: gap 0.25s var(--ease), color 0.25s var(--ease);
  }
  .svc-cat:hover .svc-cat-cta {
    gap: 14px;
    color: var(--terra);
  }

  /* ─── FLAGSHIP BAND (INDIBA) ──────────────────────── */
  .svc-flagship {
    background: var(--dark);
    color: #fff;
    padding: 96px 0;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .svc-flagship-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 64px;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .svc-flagship-img {
    border-radius: 2px;
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 5;
  }
  .svc-flagship-img img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }
  .svc-flagship h2 {
    color: #fff;
    font-size: clamp(34px, 4.5vw, 56px);
    line-height: 1.05;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .svc-flagship h2 em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--gold);
  }
  .svc-flagship p {
    font-size: 17px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.78);
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }
  .svc-flagship-meta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 32px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    padding-top: 24px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
  }
  .svc-flagship-meta-item {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
  }
  .svc-flagship-meta-item strong {
    display: block;
    color: var(--gold);
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  /* ─── TRUST STRIP ─────────────────────────────────── */
  .svc-trust {
    background: var(--sand);
    padding: 56px 0;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .svc-trust-stars { color: var(--gold); font-size: 22px; letter-spacing: 2px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .svc-trust-rating {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--dark);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .svc-trust-rating strong { color: var(--terra); font-weight: 500; }
  .svc-trust-sub { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-mid); letter-spacing: 0.04em; }

  /* ─── FINAL CTA ───────────────────────────────────── */
  .svc-final-cta {
    padding: 120px 0;
    text-align: center;
    background: var(--ivory);
  }
  .svc-final-cta h2 {
    font-size: clamp(32px, 4.5vw, 52px);
    line-height: 1.1;
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto 20px;
  }
  .svc-final-cta p {
    font-size: 17px;
    color: var(--text-mid);
    max-width: 540px;
    margin: 0 auto 36px;
  }
  .svc-final-cta-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  /* ─── LEGACY SEPARATOR ────────────────────────────── */
  .svc-legacy-divider {
    background: var(--ivory);
    padding: 64px 0 0;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .svc-legacy-divider .eyebrow { margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .svc-legacy-divider h2 {
    font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 44px);
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .svc-legacy-divider p {
    color: var(--text-mid);
    max-width: 540px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    font-size: 15px;
  }

  /* ─── LEGACY CATALOG (preservado para anchors + detalle) ─── */
  .cat-nav {
    position: sticky;
    top: 88px;
    z-index: 100;
    background: var(--ivory);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 0;
    margin-top: 56px;
  }
  .cat-nav::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    right: 0;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 48px;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, var(--ivory));
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  .cat-nav-inner {
    overflow-x: auto;
    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
    scrollbar-width: none;
    padding: 12px 48px 12px 24px;
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .cat-nav-inner::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }
  .cat-nav-pills { display: flex; gap: 8px; white-space: nowrap; }
  .cat-nav-pill {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 6px 16px;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 40px;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    color: var(--text-mid);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .cat-nav-pill:hover, .cat-nav-pill.active {
    background: var(--terra);
    color: #fff;
    border-color: var(--terra);
  }

  .cat-section {
    padding: 64px 0 80px;
    scroll-margin-top: 150px;
  }
  .cat-section:nth-child(even) { background: var(--sand); }
  .cat-header { margin-bottom: 48px; }
  .cat-header .eyebrow { margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .cat-header h2 { font-size: clamp(24px, 4vw, 36px); margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .cat-header p { color: var(--text-mid); font-size: 15px; max-width: 560px; }

  .cat-visual {
    width: 100%;
    height: 260px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .cat-visual img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; display: block; }
  .cat-visual::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(26,18,8,0.35) 0%, transparent 60%);
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  .trat-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 28px;
  }
  .trat-card {
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 2px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    transition: transform 0.25s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease;
    scroll-margin-top: 160px;
  }
  .trat-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  }
  .trat-card-img { width: 100%; height: 200px; object-fit: cover; display: block; background: var(--bg-light); }
  .trat-card--bare { border-top: 3px solid var(--terra); }
  .trat-card-body { padding: 24px; flex: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; }
  .trat-card-name {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.3;
    color: var(--dark);
    margin: 0;
  }
  .trat-card-desc { font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.65; color: var(--text-mid); margin: 0; }
  .trat-card-incluye { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px; }
  .trat-card-incluye li {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text-mid);
    padding-left: 14px;
    position: relative;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .trat-card-incluye li::before {
    content: '✓';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--terra);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 11px;
  }
  .trat-card-meta {
    margin-top: auto;
    padding-top: 16px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
  }
  .trat-duracion {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 5px;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    color: var(--text-mid);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .trat-duracion svg { width: 13px; height: 13px; flex-shrink: 0; stroke: var(--terra); }
  .trat-cta {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--terra-dk);
    text-decoration: none;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    padding: 0;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .trat-cta:hover { color: var(--terra); }

  /* ─── RESPONSIVE ──────────────────────────────────── */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) { .trat-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .svc-index-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 24px; }
    .svc-flagship-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
    .svc-flagship-img { aspect-ratio: 16/10; }
    .svc-cat-img { height: 220px; }
    .svc-cat-body { padding: 24px 24px 28px; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .svc-hero { padding: 64px 0 48px; }
    .svc-flagship { padding: 64px 0; }
    .svc-final-cta { padding: 80px 0; }
    .trat-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .cat-section { padding: 48px 0 64px; }
    .cat-header { margin-bottom: 32px; }
    .cat-visual { height: 180px; }
  }
</style>

<!-- BREADCRUMB -->
<div class="breadcrumb">
  <div class="container">
    <a href="{{ '/' | url }}">Inicio</a>
    <span>›</span>
    <span>Servicios</span>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="svc-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="eyebrow">Catálogo · 8 especialidades</span>
    <h1>Ocho especialidades,<br><em>un único oficio.</em></h1>
    <p class="lead">Tres generaciones diseñando, ejecutando y supervisando cada tratamiento. Aquí no contratamos becarios ni encadenamos sesiones por horarios apretados — cuando reservas, te atiende quien firma el resultado.</p>
    <div class="svc-hero-meta">
      <span class="svc-hero-stars">★★★★★</span>
      <strong>5.0 sobre 216 reseñas en Google</strong>
      <span class="dot">·</span>
      <span>{{ tratamientos.tratamientos | length }} tratamientos disponibles</span>
      <span class="dot">·</span>
      <span>Diagnóstico inicial gratuito</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- INDEX GRID -->
<section class="svc-index">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="svc-index-grid">

      {%- set catImages = {
        "limpiezas-faciales":   { "img": "fotoscatalogoanylopez/limpiezafacial",         "label": "Higiene + cuidado regular" },
        "tratamientos-faciales":{ "img": "fotoscatalogoanylopez/dermapen",               "label": "Renovación · Anti-acné · Manchas" },
        "lifting-antiaging":    { "img": "fotoscatalogoanylopez/ultherapyfacial",        "label": "Reafirmación sin cirugía" },
        "inyectables":          { "img": "fotoscatalogoanylopez/rellenoacidohialuronico","label": "Medicina estética avanzada" },
        "corporal":             { "img": "tratamientos/maderoterapia",                   "label": "Cuerpo · Tonicidad · Recuperación" },
        "masajes":              { "img": "tratamientos/masajes",                         "label": "Manual · Terapéutico · Drenaje" },
        "estetica-decorativa":  { "img": "tratamientos/micropigmentacion",               "label": "Pestañas · Micropigmentación" },
        "depilacion":           { "img": "tratamientos/depilacion-ipl",                  "label": "IPL · Pieles cómodas" }
      } -%}

      {%- set catSubpages = {
        "limpiezas-faciales":    "/services/limpiezas-faciales/",
        "tratamientos-faciales": "/services/tratamientos-faciales/",
        "lifting-antiaging":     "/services/lifting-antiaging/",
        "inyectables":           "/services/inyectables/",
        "corporal":              "/services/corporal/",
        "masajes":               "/services/masajes/",
        "estetica-decorativa":   "/services/estetica-decorativa/",
        "depilacion":            "/services/depilacion/"
      } -%}

      {% for cat in tratamientos.categorias %}
        {%- set catTrats = tratamientos.tratamientos | byCategory(cat.id) -%}
        {%- set imgInfo = catImages[cat.id] -%}
        {%- set imgPath = imgInfo.img -%}
        {%- set isFlag = cat.id == "lifting-antiaging" -%}
        {%- set padded = "0" + (loop.index | string) if loop.index < 10 else (loop.index | string) -%}
        {%- set total = "0" + (tratamientos.categorias | length | string) if (tratamientos.categorias | length) < 10 else (tratamientos.categorias | length | string) -%}
        {%- set subUrl = catSubpages[cat.id] -%}
        {%- set catHref = (subUrl | url) if subUrl else ("#" + cat.id) -%}

        <a href="{{ catHref }}" class="svc-cat" data-cat="{{ cat.id }}">
          <div class="svc-cat-img">
            <span class="svc-cat-num">{{ padded }} / {{ total }}</span>
            {% if isFlag %}<span class="svc-cat-flag">Especialidad estrella</span>{% endif %}
            <picture>
              <source srcset="{{ ('/images/' + imgPath + '.webp') | url }}" type="image/webp">
              <img
                src="{{ ('/images/' + imgPath + '.png') | url }}"
                alt="{{ cat.nombre }} en AnyLopez Benidorm"
                loading="{{ 'eager' if loop.index <= 2 else 'lazy' }}"
                decoding="async"
                width="640"
                height="360"
              />
            </picture>
          </div>
          <div class="svc-cat-body">
            <span class="svc-cat-eyebrow">{{ imgInfo.label }}</span>
            <h2 class="svc-cat-name">{{ cat.nombre }}</h2>
            <p class="svc-cat-desc">{{ cat.descripcion }}</p>
            <p class="svc-cat-trat-list">
              {%- set tratNamesStr = "" -%}
              {%- for t in catTrats -%}
                {%- if loop.first -%}
                  {%- set tratNamesStr = t.nombre -%}
                {%- else -%}
                  {%- set tratNamesStr = tratNamesStr + " · " + t.nombre -%}
                {%- endif -%}
              {%- endfor -%}
              {{ catTrats | length }} tratamiento{{ "s" if catTrats | length > 1 else "" }} ·
              {{ tratNamesStr | truncate(110, true, "…") }}
            </p>
            <span class="svc-cat-cta">Ver tratamientos <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></span>
          </div>
        </a>
      {% endfor %}

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- TRUST STRIP -->
<section class="svc-trust">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="svc-trust-stars">★★★★★</div>
    <div class="svc-trust-rating"><strong>5.0</strong> · 216 reseñas verificadas en Google</div>
    <div class="svc-trust-sub">Más de 30 años acompañando pacientes en Benidorm</div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FLAGSHIP — INDIBA -->
<section class="svc-flagship">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="svc-flagship-grid">
      <div class="svc-flagship-img">
        <picture>
          <source srcset="{{ '/images/fotoscatalogoanylopez/radiofrecuenciacorporal.webp' | url }}" type="image/webp">
          <img
            src="{{ '/images/fotoscatalogoanylopez/radiofrecuenciacorporal.png' | url }}"
            alt="Radiofrecuencia INDIBA en AnyLopez Benidorm"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
            width="800"
            height="1000"
          />
        </picture>
      </div>
      <div>
        <span class="eyebrow" style="color: var(--gold);">Tratamiento bandera</span>
        <h2>Radiofrecuencia INDIBA — <em>el lifting que no se nota</em>.</h2>
        <p>Si has cuidado tu piel toda la vida pero los espejos te devuelven flacidez, INDIBA es la respuesta sin quirófano. Tecnología CRet/RES que estimula tu propio colágeno desde la primera sesión. Indoloro, sin recuperación, compatible con todo lo demás.</p>
        <div class="svc-flagship-meta">
          <div class="svc-flagship-meta-item">
            <strong>350 €</strong>
            Pack 10 sesiones
          </div>
          <div class="svc-flagship-meta-item">
            <strong>525 €</strong>
            Ahorro vs sesión suelta
          </div>
          <div class="svc-flagship-meta-item">
            <strong>1ª sesión</strong>
            Resultados visibles
          </div>
        </div>
        <a href="{{ '/radiofrecuencia/' | url }}" class="btn btn-accent">Conocer INDIBA →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- LEGACY DIVIDER -->
<section class="svc-legacy-divider">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="eyebrow">Catálogo completo</span>
    <h2>Listado por especialidad</h2>
    <p>Mientras estrenamos las páginas dedicadas de cada especialidad, aquí tienes el catálogo completo con detalle de cada tratamiento.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- LEGACY CATEGORY NAV -->
<nav class="cat-nav" aria-label="Categorías de tratamientos">
  <div class="cat-nav-inner">
    <div class="cat-nav-pills">
      {% for cat in tratamientos.categorias %}
      <a href="#{{ cat.id }}" class="cat-nav-pill">{{ cat.nombre }}</a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- LEGACY TREATMENT CATEGORIES (preserved for anchor links and full detail) -->
{% for cat in tratamientos.categorias %}
{% set catTrats = tratamientos.tratamientos | byCategory(cat.id) %}
<section class="cat-section" id="{{ cat.id }}">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cat-header">
      <span class="eyebrow">{{ loop.index }} / {{ tratamientos.categorias | length }}</span>
      <h2>{{ cat.nombre }}</h2>
      <p>{{ cat.descripcion }}</p>
    </div>

    {% set catSharedImage = catTrats | length > 1 and catTrats[0].imagen == catTrats[1].imagen %}
    {% if catSharedImage %}
    {% set catImg0 = catTrats[0].imagen %}
    <div class="cat-visual">
